      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; qualitative confirmation that validation inputs are representative of COU inputs.",
      "rationale": "Validation and COU share identical pump geometry, operating flow-speed envelope, and blood analog fluid properties. No significant differences in input parameters between validation context and COU context identified. Formal equivalency mapping not required at MRL 2; qualitative confirmation satisfies Gradation 1."
